{"article_id":"Dfq9OsfZpdhrqxeE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"NASHUA , N.H. -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Ties between Florida Sen. Marco Rubio and former Florida Gov . Jeb Bush , political allies for more than a decade , are fraying","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"as the Republican presidential campaign picks up .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"In public , mentor Bush and protege Rubio have avoided criticizing each other","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"since Rubio announced his candidacy .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"But Bush allies have started quietly spreading negative information about Rubio ' s record .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Also , supporters of the two Miami politicians are drawing contrasts between Rubio , a 43-year-old son of Cuban immigrants , and 62-year-old Bush , a member of one of the nation ' s most powerful political dynasties .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"\" Sparks are going to fly , \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"said Al Cardenas , a Bush adviser","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"who is also close to Rubio .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"\" For the first time in our country ' s history you ' ve got two guys from the same town in the same state from same party","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"running in the same primary . \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"He added :","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"\" You can bet that","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"regardless of how nice Jeb or Marco wants to be ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"their staffs are going to do anything","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"they can","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"to win . \"","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"As Bush tries to convince Republicans of his conservative credentials ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"supporters are asserting","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that as governor , he was far more conservative than Rubio","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"when both held prominent state posts .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Rubio served as Florida House speaker in the two years","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"immediately after Bush left the governor ' s mansion .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Bush viewed Rubio as a protector of his political legacy .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"The governor presented Rubio with a golden sword in a ceremony","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"symbolizing a political handoff nearly a decade ago , an endorsement","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"that Rubio ' s advisers point to","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"when asked about the Bush camp ' s early aggression now .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"\" I have it somewhere at home , \"","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Rubio said of the sword .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Asked about it","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"while campaigning in New Hampshire on the weekend ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"he suggested","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"the keepsake is not prominently displayed in his house .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" I have young kids .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"I don ' t want them running around with a sword , \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"They still call each other friends .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"But subtle criticism has emerged","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"as Rubio speaks of the need","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"to break with ideas from the last century","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and Bush questions","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"whether one term in the Senate can prepare anyone for the White House .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Rubio ' s respect for Bush is well-documented in his writings and years of political activity","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"when he relied on Bush ' s support , donor network and even former staff","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to help his own rise .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Rubio said","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"he would not enter Florida ' s 2010 Senate contest","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"were Bush to run ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and Bush didn ' t .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Rubio was expected to defer to Bush again in the 2016 presidential contest","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"once Bush began preparing for the race .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Instead , Rubio this past week announced his own presidential campaign in their hometown ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"insisting","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"the stakes were too high for him to \" wait his turn. \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Bush has not declared his candidacy","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"but is expected to .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Rubio ' s move forced prominent Florida Republicans such as Cardenas to pick sides .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Bush \" feels disappointed","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"because he ' s cared for him for so long , \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"said Cardenas ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"who attended Rubio ' s wedding .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"\" You just don ' t want to go to battle against someone","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"you care for . \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Several former Florida legislators","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"now aligned with Bush","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"challenged Rubio ' s conservative credentials during his time as speaker .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"In the Senate , Rubio has opposed taxpayer-financed special projects","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"known as earmarks .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"But he supported them as a state legislator ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"these critics point out ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"in one year alone requesting $ 43 million in such spending for public works , autism and substance abuse programs .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"\" Bush was more conservative , \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"said U.S. Rep. Dennis Ross , R-Fla. ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"who served in the Legislature with Rubio","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"and","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"while Bush was governor ,","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"and now supports Bush .","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"Ross highlighted Bush ' s aggressive use of the line-item veto","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"to cut government spending ,","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"regardless of whether such spending benefited members of his own party .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Former state Rep. Juan-Carlos Planas ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"who also worked with both men","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and now backs Bush ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"made a similar point .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" There were always projects","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"that were important to Marco ' s constituents , \"","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"\" And they always ended up in the budget . \"","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Rubio ' s team declined to respond to those statements","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"and hasn ' t cast Bush or other rivals in a negative light .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Yet a prominent Rubio supporter , billionaire businessman Norman Braman , has been less diplomatic .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"\" We have to look for the future , \"","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Braman told CNN this past week in a round of interviews .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"\" We have to go beyond the Bushes .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"We have to go beyond the Clintons. \"","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"He added :","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"\" We ' re not a country","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"that believes in dynasties . \"","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"Bush and Rubio courted New Hampshire primary voters on the same stage , hours apart Friday ,","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"but did not cross paths .","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"\" He is a good , close friend , \"","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Bush said .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"\" It is what it is . \"","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"\" Jeb Bush is my friend , \"","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Rubio said .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"\" This is a race .","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"It ' ll be a competitive environment . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":217,"left":0,"right":216,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":216,"left":207,"right":215,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":125,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":110,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":112,"right":123,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":111,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":111,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":114,"right":121,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":7,"right":113,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":115,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":12,"right":119,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":13,"right":118,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":14,"right":117,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":145,"right":205,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":144,"right":38,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":128,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":18,"right":127,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":19,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent